{"tid":2121313,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈迎擊惡意網民！「不會就此罷手，會繼續抓下去」","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T16:41:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c40a72013d835b572813b8b40a24ef1fc571951e","tid":2121313,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"一向做自己的希澈，最近也公開對惡意網民宣戰，霸氣十足的方式果然充滿宇宙大明星的風格！<br />\n<br />\n希澈昨晚在自己的 Instagram 上發出一張訴狀的照片，開門見山地表示：「我不會寬貸。就算要和解，我也會一概交給律師處理。謝謝鄭率律師和江南警察局的搜查官，我不會就此罷手，一定會繼續抓惡意網民。」<br />\n<br />\n在簡單明瞭地表達完回擊惡意網民的意志後，希澈也感性地向粉絲道謝：「謝謝那些跟令人無言的惡意網友奮戰到底、搜集資料支持我的粉絲⋯⋯你們明明應該是最難受的人⋯⋯真的很感謝你麼^-^。」<br />\n<br />\n在貼文的最後，希澈也不忘逗趣地說：「以後我也會繼續當有點討人厭但不會闖禍的宇宙大明星金希澈！！」"},{"pid":"fa61a77ef037d61cfd2e2e082edb7bbf52d423f4","tid":2121313,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6d508f9d3278add96bd45560a2c7c216/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-07-23/128580-858016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6d508f9d3278add96bd45560a2c7c216%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-07-23%2F128580-858016.jpg&h=a6721dc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46b039a41ff5593fba8f496cf4461fa7eb86a5bb","tid":2121313,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"在貼文的最後，希澈也不忘逗趣地說：「以後我也會繼續當有點討人厭但不會闖禍的宇宙大明星金希澈！！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3eTJEIic5hmVDVc0UZ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3eTJEIic5hmVDVc0UZ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=d8ffd0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQaOHUK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQaOHUK.gif&h=b424ed20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a30488a8d88f4adaac0b75ed7f6042466b60df6e","tid":2121313,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:37:29.000Z","msg":"